snippet.title: Amber Melanie Smith
snippet.description:
Tips and strategies to help aspiring change makers change the world and live a life of impact and purpose! Whether you're trying to make a social impact...

By growing or starting a nonprofit or volunteer organization
Through social entrepreneurship or a socially responsible company
By finding volunteer opportunities to lend your time and talents 
By investing in social change as a philanthropist
By raising your voice as an activist
By being (or raising) an overall awesome, kind person who does good things 

...This channel is for you! Subscribe for a new video each week.

The information contained in these videos is for educational and entertainment purposes only.
